197
00:12:24,500 --> 00:12:26,260
Biar saya tengok kepakaran awak.

198
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:30,100
Awak tunggu.

199
00:12:45,490 --> 00:12:46,300
Keluarlah.

200
00:12:51,370 --> 00:12:52,700
Kenapa awak suruh saya keluar?

201
00:12:52,980 --> 00:12:54,580
Awak tak takut orang lain perasan?

202
00:12:57,420 --> 00:12:59,060
Apa masalahnya kalau orang lain nampak pesakit?

203
00:12:59,570 --> 00:13:00,540
Pesakit?

204
00:13:01,020 --> 00:13:01,820
Siapa pesakit?

205
00:13:06,500 --> 00:13:07,260
Saya?

206
00:13:08,940 --> 00:13:11,420
Jika tidak, bagaimana Song Yiju menunjukkan kepakarannya?

207
00:13:12,620 --> 00:13:14,220
Maksud awak, biar Song Yiju cucuk saya?

208
00:13:16,580 --> 00:13:17,180
Awak lihat

209
